# Strict CSS Rules for AI Agents

The AI agent is STRICTLY FORBIDDEN from ever writing inline styles (e.g., `style="..."`) in HTML or Markdown files. 
You must always use the central CSS variables defined in `assets/css/style.css` (or other global stylesheets) for any layout or visual adjustments. 
Do not introduce new hardcoded hex, RGB values, or inline fonts in the project files. 
All visual modifications must be achieved through reusable CSS classes and variables.